      • getFullScientificName

        public String getFullScientificName()
        The method tries to best assemble the most complete scientific name possible incl the name authorship. It first tries to use scientificName and scientificNameAuthorship if existing. Otherwise it uses the atomized name parts. Warning: this uses the genus property which might be wrong in case of synonym names, see https://code.google.com/p/darwincore/issues/detail?id=151 Note also that the assembled name never includes a rank marker.
        Returns:
        the best guess of the full scientific name with authorship

      • getProperty

        public String getProperty(org.gbif.dwc.terms.Term prop)
        Gets a dwc property by its concept term. This method is only able to access official Darwin Core or Dublin Core terms, not any custom extensions.
        Parameters:
        prop - the concept term to lookup
        Returns:
        the terms value, null or IllegalArgumentException for unsupported terms
